name: Bullion Vase L — KIFU PARIS
description: The Bullion Vase is a classic and elegant piece, handmade with Shagreen & Pen Shell, and bronze-patina brass. All interior of KIFU PARIS vases can support water. It requires care to wipe clean with a soft dry cloth and is made in the Philippines. The use of natural components may cause color variants in the stingray and other exotic finishes, showcasing the luxurious authenticity of the products.
